SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 32 - Museum Construction Delayed by
 Ancient Pump Curse
DESCRIPTION:Back to the construction site where the machinery may actually
 be haunted. We're trying to make progress... assuming the pump doesn't
 fight back again. Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better than
 ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to the
 franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on your
 own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2Frd5kk047I
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23422211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260506T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260531T164400Z
DTSTART:20260527T203000Z
DTEND:20260527T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 1 - Siege of Tobruk
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new sniper campaign begins! Desert warfare, stealth
 tactics, long-distance shots, and hopefully fewer panic moments than
 usual. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that combines
 stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge, open
 levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=09NtJ39Ncbc
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23432211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260507T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260531T164400Z
DTSTART:20260528T203000Z
DTEND:20260528T223000Z
SUMMARY:Outbound | Ep. 1 - Warm Lights, Open Roads, Fresh Beginnings
DESCRIPTION:Another brand-new series kicks off! Cozy road-trip vibes,
 exploration, and the promise of peaceful journeys under warm evening
 skies. Explore a colourful world and build your own cosy home on wheels.
 Craft workstations, and source energy from the sun, wind, or water.
 Upgrade and customize your vehicle, grow crops, and live sustainably
 off-grid with up to 4 players.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PGMzCQ8jfpI
CATEGORIES:Outbound
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
