SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 33 - The Concrete Pump Has Become
 Self-Aware
DESCRIPTION:Back to the construction site where the machinery now appears
 to have opinions of its own. We're building, troubleshooting, and possibly
 negotiating with heavy equipment. Construction Simulator is back - bigger
 and better than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them
 brand new to the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge
 maps - on your own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
