SUMMARY:Outbound | Ep. 2 - Powered by Tea and Solar Panels
DESCRIPTION:Back on the open road for another cozy road-trip adventure.
 Warm lights, quiet journeys, and enough tea to keep the van running...
 probably. Explore a colourful world and build your own cosy home on
 wheels. Craft workstations, and source energy from the sun, wind, or
 water. Upgrade and customize your vehicle, grow crops, and live
 sustainably off-grid with up to 4 players.
